title: Watch The Lemon Twigs Perform “I Wanna Prove To You” On Colbert - Stereogum
text:
James Rettig @jmret | 9:17 am Share < br />this article: 
The Lemon Twigs made their second late-night TV appearance in support of their debut album, Do Hollywood , last night after one on Fallon back in September. This time, they were performing for Colbert alongside house band Jon Batiste & Stay Human, and they did “I Wanna Prove To You,” which recently got its own music video . Watch their appearance below. 
Do Hollywood is out now via 4AD.
